    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were scoped out as not required at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 was confirmed at all 5 operating points, satisfying the pre-specified acceptance criterion. The assessment team accepts the simulation results in support of the regulatory submission.",
